---
title: Crunchtastic Game Day Chicken Strips with Creamy Bacon Slaw
description: Get your game face on because this recipe goes the distance! Coated with crunchy corn flakes, these crispy "boneless wings" bring all your favourite game day flavours and leave the messy bones at the sidelines!
